you may ran out of allocated space locally for your docker engine
+1 to shiqi’s suggestion, i usually need to run `docker system prune` when i see this https://stackoverflow.com/a/59141204
thanks! that seems to have fixed the redis build error, and @Ashwin’s PR from <#C03QNBU7YQ5|> fixed my OCR service build, so all is well again :smile: appreciate the help
